@WonderwallMSN Thanks so much! Goodnight!
@WonderwallMSN Michael C. Hall. I mean, I guess I'm crushing more on Dexter at the moment. It must be the whole mass murderer thing. Sighhh.
@WonderwallMSN All my friends back home, friends in other bands, Betsey Johnson, Ellen DeGeneres, Glenn Danzig and McAlisters Deli.
@WonderwallMSN I want to stay open minded, positive, and never forget where I came from. Oh, and I wanna be in this band forever too.
@WonderwallMSN We're about to head to Japan... I <3 it there.
@WonderwallMSN There's no downside to playing anywhere. And it's really hard to pick a favorite.

@WonderwallMSN Of course! Josh is the biggest fan out of all of us.
@WonderwallMSN I hope I never get used to red carpets... It's pretty fun playing dress up. I just hope I don't fall in my heels.
@WonderwallMSN To answer your question, I don't know just yet!
@WonderwallMSN Haha... I was hoping to find out what she's wearing and wear a carbon copy. Then we could become best friends
@WonderwallMSN We were in the UK on a headlining run for our new record. Honestly, I thought it was just a rumor. So stoked it wasn't.
@WonderwallMSN I'm a new fan... It took me a while to accept the fact that I am totally stupefied by her.
@WonderwallMSN So stoked for it. I really want to meet Lady Gaga.
@WonderwallMSN Let's go!
